comments.text: Vanoss is absolutely ridiculous. Speedy was around long before him. Vanoss copied his video style, even down to the same games. Vanoss himself is alright, but the people he plays with are extremely annoying. They all laugh like hyenas when something stupid happens to someone's body in a game. They all seem childish and immature. Speedy's friends are all unique and they all have such great chemistry. I will say speedy isn't as good as he used to be since they all switched to pc gaming and basically the only game they play now is cs go, but Vanoss' videos have always seemed childish and the funny moments have always seemed scripted and pre planned, but speed us videos seem genuine. I've always thought Vanoss has so many subs because his channel appeals to the millions of 8-10 year old kids on YouTube. Bottom line is there would be no Vanoss without speedy. My loyalty is with the Crew
